cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.HC, cs.SOC, cs.CC 

This paper discusses the phenomenon of Facebook addiction among university students, which involves the intersection of computer science, social media, and human behavior. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CY (Computers and Society), followed by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), cs.SOC (Social and Economic Networks), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
